$NetBSD: MESSAGE,v 1.4 2006/06/13 09:27:27 martin Exp $

Before you install ${PREFIX}/share/examples/mini_sendmail/mailer.conf
as /etc/mailer.conf, edit it to replace ``relayhost'' with the name of
the smart mail relay host.

You probably will also want to set check_mailq=NO in /etc/daily.conf.

See the manual page for details.

===========================================================================
